Thanks [~rohithsharma] for sharing the patch.
Generally patch looks good.

Few minor nits:
1. 
{noformat}
private CompoundComparator fifoComparator;
{noformat}
I feel this variable is not needed in {{FifoOrderingPolicy}}

2. Also in {{PriorityComparator}} if needed we can remove the temporary variable {{res}}.
3. {{TestFifoOrderingPolicy}}, could u pls add a case where priority is null too. Since we have a comparator, its good we have a case for all corner cases.

